- "SCOTUS has caused more repression and racism in this nation than any other group of people in America. #DredScott #Marriage #SemST" → 'none'

Use the guidance above to maximize correct classification and minimize confusion between the 'against', 'favor', and 'none' labels, especially in cases of implicit or ambiguous texts.
